    <h1>Creating variations</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Do you have products that need to be imported into plentymarkets? And to complicate things even further: Do you sell these products in different sizes and colours?</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You might already know that plentymarkets has an import tool.
But you might not have tried your hand at a realistic example yet.
This page of the manual guides you step by step through the process of importing new items and variations in plentymarkets.
This page relies on an example sync, which you can download and import into your own system.</p>
</div>
<div id="requirements" class="admonitionblock tip">
<table>
