<p>This page assumes that you already have a basic understanding of the <a href="/en/data/importing-data/ElasticSync">import tool</a>. Furthermore, make sure you’ve saved the following data in your system before you start importing items and variations:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p><a href="/en/item/settings/attributes">Attributes and attribute values</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="/en/item/settings/categories">Categories</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="/en/item/settings/prices">Sales prices</a></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</div>
