<h2 id="100">1. Downloading the example files</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>This page of the manual guides you step by step through the process of importing new items and variations in plentymarkets. This page relies on two example files, which you can download and import into your own system.</p>
</div>
